# {{ ts_project_root }}/ ‚Äî TypeScript backend service

Node/TS service (Express) with the same conventions as the Python side: an
app factory (`{{ ts_source_root }}/app.ts`, what tests import) split from the
entrypoint (`{{ ts_source_root }}/index.ts`), a `/health` route, and full
tooling ‚Äî eslint flat config, `tsc --noEmit` typecheck, Jest + ts-jest +
supertest.

Workflow (from the project root): `make ts-install`, then `make ts-dev` /
`make ts-lint` / `make ts-typecheck` / `make ts-test` / `make ts-build`.

